videos.description: Mike Daum flushes a fast-break dunk for South Dakota State.
videos.headline: Daum throws down fast-break jam

videos.description: Mike Daum hit a tough shot to move up to eight on the NCAA all-time scoring list then gets a huge block on the other end of the court for South Dakota State.
videos.headline: Daum achieves a milestone and gets it done on both ends

videos.description: Dylan Osetkowski hits a tough hook shot to give Texas a 3-point lead over South Dakota State.
videos.headline: Osetkowski 's jump hook extends Texas' lead
